-- Lloyds Said to Plan Sale of Covered Bonds in Pounds
-- B y   B e n   M a r t i n
-- 2012-01-19T13:14:18Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-19/lloyds-said-to-plan-sale-of-covered-bonds-in-pounds.html
Lloyds Banking Group Plc (LLOY)  plans to
sell covered bonds in pounds, according to a banker involved in
the transaction.  BNP Paribas SA, Royal Bank of Scotland Group Plc,  Banco
Santander SA (SAN)  and UBS AG are managing the deal with Lloyds, the
banker said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Ben Martin at 
 bmartin38@bloomberg.net  